      "title": "Eliminate x",
      "content": "Eliminate $x$.<br/>$$2(5x+12y=52)$$<br/>$$10x+24y=104$$<br/>$$(10x+24y)-(10x+6y)=104-32$$<br/>$$18y=72$$<br/>$$y=4$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Solve for x",
      "content": "Substitute.<br/>$$5x+12(4)=52$$<br/>$$5x+48=52$$<br/>$$x=0.8$$"
    },
